<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFAitchison1999">Aitchison, Jean (1999) [1995]. <i>Linguistics: An Introduction</i> (2nd ed.). London: Hodder &amp; Stoughton.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Linguistics%3A+An+Introduction&amp;rft.aulast=Aitchison&amp;rft.aufirst=Jean&amp;rft.au=Aitchison%2C+Jean&amp;rft.date=1999&amp;rft.edition=2nd&amp;rft.place=London&amp;rft.pub=Hodder+%26+Stoughton&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Linguistics"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFAkmajian2001">Akmajian, Adrian (2001). <i>Linguistics</i>. et al. MIT Press. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0262511231" class="internal">ISBN 0-262-51123-1</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Linguistics&amp;rft.aulast=Akmajian&amp;rft.aufirst=Adrian&amp;rft.au=Akmajian%2C+Adrian&amp;rft.date=2001&amp;rft.pub=MIT+Press&amp;rft.isbn=0-262-51123-1&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Linguistics"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFGriniewiczElwira_M._Dubieniec2004">Griniewicz, Sergiusz; Elwira M. Dubieniec (2004). <i>Introduction To Linguistics</i> (2nd ed.). Białystok, WSFiZ. pp.&#160;91.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Introduction+To+Linguistics&amp;rft.aulast=Griniewicz&amp;rft.aufirst=Sergiusz&amp;rft.au=Griniewicz%2C+Sergiusz&amp;rft.au=Elwira+M.+Dubieniec&amp;rft.date=2004&amp;rft.pages=pp.%26nbsp%3B91&amp;rft.edition=2nd&amp;rft.pub=Bia%C5%82ystok%2C+WSFiZ&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Linguistics"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
